title: StartButler
body:
Good evening my lady. I trust everything is to your liking?
[[Yes, did you string up the lovely decorations?|ButlerGood01]]
[[Yes, could you get me a drink?.|ButlerNeutral01]]
[[Yes, but I feel I haven't spent enough time with Graf Von Azabu. |ButlerBad01]]

title: ButlerGood01
body:
Yes, I had to use some heavy rope. 
[[You must be exhausted. Perhaps you should take a break.|ButlerGood02]]
[[Ok. Could you make me a Hanky Panky, please?|ButlerNeutral02]]
[[That Graf must keep you all tied up!|ButlerBad02]]

title: ButlerBad01
body:
Maybe some liquid courage, my lady?
[[Yes, a Hanky Panky, please.|ButlerNeutral02]]
[[Yes, what about a Virgin Mary, please.|ButlerBad02]]
[[Just water for me, please.|ButlerBad02]]

title: ButlerNeutral01
body:
Certainly. What's your preference? 
[[A Bloody Mary, please.|ButlerGood02]]
[[A Hanky Panky to get in the mood, please.|ButlerNeutral02]]
[[I'll have what the Graf is drinking, please.|ButlerBad02]]

title: ButlerGood02
body:
Thank you. Anything else?
Bloody Mary/break 
[[Could you tell the Graf to meet me on the balcony, please?|ButlerGoodEnding]]
[[Could you put in a good word for me with the Gr√§fin?|ButlerGoodEnding]]
[[Thank you, that'll be all for now.|ButlerNeutralEnding]]

title: ButlerNeutral02
body:
Anything else? 
hanky panky
[[Yes, another one please!|ButlerNeutralEnding]]
[[Thank you, that'll be all for now.|ButlerNeutralEnding]]
[[Just leave me alone now!|ButlerBadEnding]]

This explains your butch forarms.

title: ButlerBad02
body:
You seem very interested in the Graf. 
Count's drink/ tied up
[[I'm interested in many things.|ButlerNeutralending]]
[[Yes, that's why I'm here.|ButlerBadEnding]]
[[What do you think?.|ButlerBadEnding]]

title: ButlerGoodEnding
body: Most certainly, my lady! Enjoy your evening.

title: ButlerNeutralEnding
body: As you wish, my lady. Enjoy your evening.
